Package: magmaan
Title: Exploratory R bindings for the magmaan C++ SEM library
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R:
    person("Jonas", "Moss", email = "jonas.moss@bi.no", role = c("aut", "cre"))
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LinkingTo: Rcpp, RcppEigen
Imports: Rcpp
SystemRequirements: C++23, NLopt
Description: Thin Rcpp wrappers exposing magmaan's C++ functions for
    interactive use. Self-contained: the C++ core (plus the vendored PORT and
    QUADPACK routines) is compiled from sources vendored under src/ and linked
    against a system NLopt, so the package installs without CMake or a prebuilt
    library. Not CRAN-bound.
